debar provides search input UI with callback to update parent state. Search results displayed in dedicated panel replacing normal per-section view when active.|\n|**Search Tests** <br> `packages/app-desktop/gui/ConfigScreen/utils/filterSettingsBySearchQuery.test.ts`|Comprehensive test suite validating filter logic: empty/whitespace queries, case-insensitive matching in label/description/key, cross-section aggregation, screen-section exclusion, and empty result handling.|\n|**Ignore Configuration** <br> `.eslintignore`, `.gitignore`|Added entries to exclude new filter utility and test file from ESLint and git tracking.|\n|**Mobile Plugin Assets** <br> `packages/app-mobile/pluginAssets/abc/abc_render.js.base64.js`, `packages/app-mobile/pluginAssets/index.js`, `packages/app-mobile/pluginAssets/index.web.js`|Updated embedded ABC notation renderer template with SVG viewBox attribute logic; updated asset hashes and reordered file entries in asset manifests.|\n|**Build Configuration** <br> `packages/lib/tsconfig.json`|Minor formatting adjustment to `exclude` array closing bracket.|\n\n## Sequence Diagram(s)\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagram\n    actor User\n    participant Sidebar\n    participant ConfigScreen\n    participant FilterUtil\n    participant UI as Rendered Results\n\n    User->>Sidebar: Types in search input\n    Sidebar->>ConfigScreen: onSearchQueryChange(query)\n    ConfigScreen->>ConfigScreen: Update searchQuery state\n    ConfigScreen->>FilterUtil: filterSettingsBySearchQuery(sections, query, device)\n    FilterUtil->>FilterUtil: Filter by label/description/key (case-insensitive)\n    FilterUtil-->>ConfigScreen: Filtered sections array\n    ConfigScreen->>UI: Render search results panel with matches\n    UI-->>User: Display filtered settings or \"No results\" message\n```\n\n</details>\n\n<!-- walkthrough_end -->\n\n\n<!-- pre_merge_checks_walkthrough_start -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- pre_merge_checks_override_start -->\n> [!IMPORTANT]\n> ## Pre-merge checks failed\n>